## How to Take Screenshots

### Using Browser DevTools

1. Open the page in Chrome/Firefox
2. Press F12 to open DevTools
3. Click device toolbar icon (or Ctrl+Shift+M)
4. Select device size or enter custom dimensions
5. Take screenshot:
   - Chrome: DevTools menu → Capture screenshot
   - Firefox: Right-click → Take a Screenshot

### Recommended Tools

- **Browser Extensions**: Full Page Screen Capture, Awesome Screenshot
- **Desktop Tools**: Snipping Tool (Windows), Screenshot (Mac)
- **Online Tools**: screely.com, screenshot.rocks

## Image Specifications

- Format: PNG (for UI) or JPG (for photos)
- Desktop: 1920px width
- Tablet: 768px width  
- Mobile: 375px width
- Quality: High (80-90%)
- File size: Optimize to < 500KB per image
